{"tid":470504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無圖，頭先撞到我果條女，正到呢⋯⋯","createTime":"2017-11-16T10:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T15:26:58.000Z","uid":56875,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"931299a48fc29e60741ac5927bc77a4f3a196a05","tid":470504,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"「唔好意思呀。」 <br />\n<br />\n道歉？正！咁即係話佢唔係惡人啦，剩機屈返筆先！ <br />\n<br />\n「喂！」我霍地站起，正想話擺出個兇神惡刹款，佔一佔先機，點知看清對方，D粗口又吞返入肚&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n眼前，係一件囡，囡就成日見丫，但係咁正就好難得。 <br />\n<br />\n只見佢斯斯文文，矮我半個頭，頭髮中等長度，戴副眼鏡，着住套裝，雖然件裇衫扣到上頸，但係咁仲正，因為胸前迫到兩粒鈕就跌咁款 ，黑色裙下係一對白滑長腿，配上整潔的高跟鞋，如果可以申請比佢踩JJ的話，高登起碼爆五個1001！ <br />\n<br />\n點樣upload圖？"},{"pid":"40f69bf2381d3a716f3d0adc0974c0258393477b","tid":470504,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20170102/photo/0102-00282-009b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170102%2Fphoto%2F0102-00282-009b4.jpg&h=24974342&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7022a74f395f8edbf9b062a4d545d6a91b66e29c","tid":470504,"uid":5077,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/190132_886e9db6680bbb8ec89a5f5da6ea44f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F190132_886e9db6680bbb8ec89a5f5da6ea44f6.jpg&h=cd63c553&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/190132_71412f184614a0dc53b65b8809e3863d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F190132_71412f184614a0dc53b65b8809e3863d.jpg&h=b78cbc06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣Up呀"},{"pid":"a187284ab2b9a04bdc4c2cb7da807743f8d37ce2","tid":470504,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime